### Description
I'm using css variables for colors.
for example:
```
:root {
--s1-N-0-color: #FFFFFF;
}
```

in prod mode it become shortened; 
```
:root {
--s1-N-0-color: #fff;
}
```

In dev mode is work as expected and it keep the hex as is.


## üî¨ Minimal Reproduction
1. Create a new angular cli project 
2. Add to styles.scss 
```
:root {
--s1-N-0-color: #FFFFFF;
}
```

3. server the project in dev mode 
4. open the browser and in the dev tools you can see the hex color changed to #fff




